<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>18</hymn_number>
<title>zài zhè xiē jǐn cún de nián jiān 迦南18</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zài zhè xiē jǐn cún de nián jiān, nǐ gāi zěn me yàng?
 nǐ shì jǐng xǐng, nǐ shì chén shuì, hái shì piào pō méi yǒu dìng xiàng?
 nǐ shì zhàn zài shì jiè? hái shì zài zhǔ de shēn páng?
 nǐ shì zhuān xīn ài zhǔ, hái shì xū dù shí guāng?
 zhǔ a qiú nǐ cì gěi wǒ men, zhì huì hé dǎn liàng,
 ràng wǒ men gēn suí nǐ de jiǎo zōng dǎ nà měi hǎo de zhàng.</lyrics>
</song>